we'll add outside quotes,

22

00:01:17,380  -->  00:01:24,250
and then we're setting this long string to our quote variable like this.

23

00:01:24,250  -->  00:01:28,900
But this will cause a syntax error when trying to initialize

24

00:01:28,900  -->  00:01:34,520
this variable because of the quotes that are inside of the outside quotes.

25

00:01:34,520  -->  00:01:36,580
When we execute this code,

26

00:01:36,580  -->  00:01:40,965
we'll see this, and it'll say "SyntaxError: invalid syntax".

27

00:01:40,965  -->  00:01:44,280
This is because the quotes are missing backslashes.

28

00:01:44,280  -->  00:01:47,920
To escape the quotes inside of the quotes,

29

